node.text: Summer’s not over yet and we’ve got the florals to keep you charged on the go 🌸 Extra battery without the extra cords. Perfect for road trips, long shifts, running errands and everywhere in between 💃🏻 We’ve got you covered! Which floral is your favorite? 🌻 Tag someone who needs this 👇 Explore the collection at www.luxylemon.com #luxylemon
